title: Anastasia's Pick 6
text:
- Hammonton at Clearview: The host Pioneers are playing a Top 10 team for the third time in four weeks. 
Pick: Hammonton, 27-17. 
- Holy Cross at Cinnaminson: In the last two seasons, the host Pirates are 0-1 against the Lancers and 13-0 against every other WJFL opponent. 
Pick: Cinnaminson, 23-20. 
- Paul VI at Winslow Township: Defensive back Melvin Reid of the host Eagles will match up with wide receivers Lonnie Moore and Stefone Moore-Green of the visiting Eagles in a clash of diminutive playmakers. 
Pick: Paul VI, 27-20. 
- Mainland at St. Augustine: The host Hermits have a physically imposing defense led by senior linebacker Jim Brady. 
Pick: St. Augustine, 34-13.
